item.title: Jas Liu
item.description: Hi, I’m Jas Liu! (Pronounced “jase”, rhymes with chase). My pronouns are they/them. I’m a Software Engineer at Radix Labs, where I help build software for the next generation of biology labs. The Radix platform helps biologists more easily achieve end-to-end automation, protocol reproducibility, automated scheduling, hardware independence, and high-volume data analysis. Find me at… email: js [at] radix.bio github: @jasopolis linkedin: liu-js Black lives matter. Black trans lives matter.
